<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<pageContent>
    <id><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D050]]></id>
	<title><![CDATA[<Introtext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0033; margin:10px -5px 10px 5px; width:738px; padding:5px 0 5px 5px; background:#e8e8e8; border-bottom:1px solid #333; display:block;">Reinforcing Value</Introtext>]]></title>
	<title2><![CDATA[]]></title2>
	<instructions><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:bold; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">How do you respond to Dr. Bennett’s concern?</welcomeText >]]></instructions>
	<choices>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[1]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[YES]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>A</b>. Confirm with Dr. Bennett his practice priorities you put into the Value Map, and lead a discussion about how addressing and controlling side effects is key to achieving positive patient outcomes. Also share that the co-pay cards may help make your product more affordable for patients.</welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="30">
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D050_A010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[2]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>B</b>. Tell Dr. Bennett that you have a co-pay card that makes your product more affordable. Walk him through the steps a patient would need to take to use the card, which will demonstrate how easy it is for patients.</welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="0">
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D050_B010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[3]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>C</b>. Tell Dr. Bennett that you were also alarmed by the high price of your product in the beginning. Then share success stories of how you have seen the benefits for patients far outweigh the costs.</span></welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="15">
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D050_C010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[4]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>D</b>. Offer to provide more information on the co-pay card.  When Dr. Bennett understands the value of the card more, he will not be concerned about the cost of the product for his patients.</span></welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="0">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D050_D010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		
	</choices>
	<summary><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">Using the Value Map to show the link back to Sunnydale Psychiatry’s practice priorities is the best way to handle this concern (Choice A). Offering to give Dr. Bennett a step-by-step description of the process to use the co-pay cards, without linking it to the practice priorities, will not resolve his concern (Choice B). Sharing a story about other customers who have had success with your product could be effective, but you would be missing an opportunity to make it more personal to Sunnydale Psychiatry’s situation and goals (Choice C). Choice D simply offers to provide more information on the topic, which should not be necessary since the co-pay cards are easy to use and to understand. Choice A is the best choice.</welcomeText>]]></summary>
</pageContent>